    "Specifically, the first process is analyzed using textual DFG descriptions of activities and sequence flows, alongside the corresponding BPMN process model.",
    "In contrast, the remaining two processes are evaluated solely through their BPMN models.We provide a brief overview of the business processes under consideration.• The initial process, called Food Delivery involves a food delivery system that receives user orders as input and verifies their status as existing clients.",
    "If they are not present in the customer database, it creates an account for them.",
    "Subsequently, the system checks the specified payment methods, assigns the processed order to an accepting rider for delivery, and communicates the estimated waiting time to the customer.",
    "Upon the rider collecting the order, a notification is sent to the client, who, upon order receipt, notifies the system accordingly."
